---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Claude plugins — biohack.net</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:       #0F0E0D;
      --surface:  #1A1816;
      --surface2: #222020;
      --border:   #2D2B29;
      --border2:  #3A3835;
      --text:     #EAE6E1;
      --muted:    #7B7670;
      --accent:   #C96442;
      --accent-l: #DC7A59;
      --code-bg:  #15141A;
      --code-txt: #C0BAB3;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
    header { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

    .logomark {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      display: block;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.625rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .byline {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }

    .byline a { color: var(--accent-l); text-decoration: none; }
    .byline a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── Global install ─────────────────────────────────── */
    .global-install {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .global-install .label {
      font-size: 0.675rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .global-install pre {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    /* ── Divider ────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    /* ── Categories ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    .category { margin-bottom: 2.75rem; }

    .category-label {
      font-size: 0.675rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    /* ── Plugin cards ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .plugin-grid { display: grid; gap: 0.625rem; }

    .plugin {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.125rem 1.375rem 1.25rem;
      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
    }

    .plugin:hover {
      border-color: var(--border2);
      background: var(--surface2);
    }

    .plugin-name {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    .plugin-desc {
      font-size: 0.825rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .plugin pre {
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 7px;
      padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
      font-family: 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
      font-size: 0.775rem;
      color: var(--code-txt);
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ── Footer ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
    footer {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      font-size: 0.775rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer a { color: var(--muted); }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--text); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <svg class="logomark" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <rect width="36" height="36" rx="8" fill="#C96442"/>
      <path d="M11 25L18 11L25 25M14 21H22" stroke="#FDEEE8" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>

    <h1>Claude plugins</h1>
    <p class="byline">
      Will's personal <a href="https://github.com/wbniv/biohack-claude">Claude Code marketplace</a>
      — skills, hooks, and extensions for daily use.
    </p>

    <div class="global-install">
      <div class="label">Add marketplace</div>
      <pre>/plugin marketplace add wbniv/biohack-claude</pre>
    </div>
  </header>

  <hr class="divider">

  <section class="category" id="techops">
    <p class="category-label">⚒ techops</p>
    <div class="plugin-grid">

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">cf-static-site</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Set up a new static site on Cloudflare — Workers + Terraform + GH Actions, or plain Pages. Two paths: full Astro stack or plain HTML.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install cf-static-site@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">new-web-apt-repo</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Provision a web-hosted signed APT repo on Cloudflare R2, backed by aptly + GitHub Actions.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install new-web-apt-repo@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">claude-housekeeping</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Audit Claude Code artifacts for drift — skills, hooks, memories, settings, and plans — across global ~/.claude and every project.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install claude-housekeeping@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">package</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Package a program as a Debian-policy-compliant .deb for a foundry-style apt repo. Handles binaries, scripts, and source packages.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install package@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">iam-bootstrap</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Set up AWS IAM credentials for a new project — Terraform user, state backend, and self-narrowing permissions.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install iam-bootstrap@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">cf-domain-setup</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Add a domain to Cloudflare on the free plan — scoped API token, zone creation, and activation polling via curl.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install cf-domain-setup@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">aws-billing-tags</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Set up AWS cost tracking, billing tags, budget alerts, and Cost Explorer for a project.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install aws-billing-tags@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="category" id="design">
    <p class="category-label">✦ design</p>
    <div class="plugin-grid">

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">import-claude-design</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Import a Claude Design export zip into site/ and deploy via tag-triggered CI.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install import-claude-design@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="category" id="personal">
    <p class="category-label">◆ personal</p>
    <div class="plugin-grid">

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">biohack-shell</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Tab colour hooks (session-start / stop / prompt-submit) and productivity slash commands from Will's personal Claude Code setup.</p>
        <pre>/plugin install biohack-shell@biohack-claude</pre>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="category" id="gnome">
    <p class="category-label">🐚 GNOME extensions</p>
    <div class="plugin-grid">

      <div class="plugin">
        <p class="plugin-name">Claude Usage Indicator</p>
        <p class="plugin-desc">Shows your Claude.ai weekly usage % in the GNOME top panel and dock.</p>
        <pre>git clone https://github.com/wbniv/claude-usage
ln -s $PWD/claude-usage/gnome-extension \
  ~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/claude-usage@indri.studio
gnome-extensions enable claude-usage@indri.studio</pre>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <a href="https://biohack.net">biohack.net</a>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
